text: From the welcoming covered front porch to the artist studio in the back yard this well designed 2 bedroom home has been updated w/original character maintained. Open living & dining, mini split keeps you cool in summer, free/standing gas stove will keep you warm in the winter. Wood floors throughout home have just been refinished, freshly pained interior. New gas range & Bosch dishwasher in the kitchen, remodeled full bathroom, laundry/utility has additional storage. Back door opens to a private backyard oasis that is ideal for entertaining w/partially covered back deck overlooking the fenced private yard, greenhouse, peach & fig trees, garden beds & studio. Location offers comfort & convenience, walking distance to the Fountain District

Huge price reduction! Come see this great home on 5 lots. Tax assessment at $836, 000. This property is perfect for vacationing, living and enjoying time on the lake. Come enjoy all that Glenhaven has to offer - seasonal pool, tennis court, clubhouse and 2 lakes for fishing and boating. All contents of house included with the sale, except for wooden boat and some personal tools.

This little gem lives large and absolutely sparkles! 3 bdrms, 1.75 baths, open floor plan with new paint & floor coverings, and a brand new custom kitchen that's a WOW . Quartz counter tops and eat-in island, farmhouse sink, shiny SS appliances and plenty of great cabinets. Ample dining & living areas, lots of windows and light, slider door opens to the deck. Primary bedroom has completely renovated ensuite with walk-in closet. 2nd & 3rd bedrooms with an updated full bath in the hall. 2 car attached garage plus lots of extra off street parking. Fully fenced back yard with outbuilding, garden beds &big entertainment deck, very private. Convenient location in established neighborhood near Lake Whatcom and Barkley Village, 10 mins to I-5

Like new stunning contemporary home in Bellingham's coveted South side neighborhood. High ceilings, large windows and countless custom features create an open, bright and flowing warm living space flooded with light in a woodsy setting. Fabulous entertainer's kitchen with full size side-by-side fridge & freezer, granite counters and abundant cabinetry. The well appointed primary suite features a huge shower, tub and walk-in closet. Numerous flex spaces include a downstairs rec room, a main floor office/extra bedroom and large upstairs bonus room. Enjoy ample extra parking areas. Hard to beat location with easy access to Interurban Trail for walking, hiking and biking to parks, waterfront and historic Fairhaven's shops, bars and restaurants.

Northern Heights neighborhood home that checks all of the boxes. Great setting in the back of a quiet cul-de-sac with a large fenced backyard with treed views & plenty of sunlight. The home itself has been completely remodeled inside & out including; new roof, new exterior paint, new milgard windows & completely new decks. Inside you will find vaulted ceilings, expansive hardwood flooring & a remodeled kitchen with quartz counters & soft close cabinets. Daylight walk-out basement with 4th bed + remodeled bath, plus huge walk-in storage space! This home runs efficiently with an updated high efficiency furnace & central A/C for summer comfort. Don't miss this turn-key home!

One level charmer in a fantastic mid-county location with a Ferndale address but within the Lynden School District. Located at the end of a lovely dead-end lane near Barbie's Berries. NO STEPS to enter the 3 bed/1.75 bath freshly updated home with English elm engineered flooring, white kitchen cabinetry, solid oak butcher block counters, & stainless steel appliances. Great floor plan with a family room & an office/4th bedroom. Large, level, and sunny quarter acre lot with large fenced backyard! Abuts a green area on one side, lending to a country feel. Neighboring homes are neat as a pin! Plenty of parking for a RV or boat! Did I mention air-conditioning? Mini-splits provide AC & heat, along with cool wood stove!

Completely renovated one-level Geneva neighborhood home, on an oversized private, tranquil lot in a quiet cul-de-sac is here! The open floor plan with vaulted ceilings and skylights greet you with a tastefully renovated kitchen and island, new bathrooms with walk-in showers, new flooring, interior and exterior paint, custom lighting throughout, new heat pump and furnace, new water heater, new decking and fenced yard. A perfect rec/play room for entertaining off the oversized two-car garage. The babbling creek behind the house will help you relax, and enjoy the low-maintenance NW yard and landscaping. All this and more just steps from world-famous Galbraith mountain trails, up the hill from Lake Whatcom, Whatcom Falls and minutes to town.

Beautiful well-maintained rambler on 9.3 acre oasis just 15 minutes from Bellingham. Enjoy westerly views of 3 private ponds w/willow trees from your kitchen, living & primary bedroom. Stock pond w/ fish for a fishermans paradise. The open floor plan boasts vaulted ceilings to maximize natural light. Double-sided fireplace built into gorgeous rock wall. Kitchen has custom hickory cabinets & large island w/ bar seating. Primary bedroom has walk-in closet w/ custom shelving & ensuite bathroom w/ double vanity, tiled shower, radiant heat & cedar sauna! Ideal floor plan w/3 large bedrooms plus separate bonus room. Oversized 2-car garage & large shed for ample storage. Fully-wired generator. High-Efficiency heat pump w/ central A/C. A must-see!

Nestled in the heart of Edgemoor, one of Bellingham's most desired neighborhoods, is this bright and spacious single-level beauty. Vaulted ceilings and very thoughtful layout. Privately situated at the end of a cul-de-sac on well manicured, landscaped lot. The most stunning, private backyard of lawns, gardens, & decks with brand new smart louvered pergola. Sunroom (w/ heated marble floors), skylights and abundant windows create a relaxed feeling of living in nature. Detached yoga/art studio or home-office has power & heat. Spacious primary bed w/ walk-in closet & stunning bath. Second ensuite. Central A/C w/ HEPA & ultra-violet filters. Desirable southside Bellingham schools & walking distance from the historic Fairhaven District.

Dont miss an opportunity to secure this rare buildable Geneva lot, with breathtaking, unobstructed views of Lake Whatcom, easy cycling access to Bellinghams renowned Galbraith Mt, and the quieter trails at Sudden Valleys Stimpson Reserve. Enjoy strolling around the neighborhood from this serene, dead end street location, or venture out to enjoy the natural beauty of Whatcom Falls Park along the short route to downtown Bellingham. Close proximity to water access along Euclid Ave and Lake Whatcom Beach off of Electric. Bellingham living at its best! Access to lot is from Columbus only please. Owner financing available.

Timeless Mid Century waterfront home. Soak in stunning year-round sunsets and island views from the panoramic picture windows or the generous deck just steps from the beach. Open concept living with a kitchen with countertop dining, massive light filled living room and dining room. Enjoy deck access from the living room and guest bedroom. Primary bedroom with a private bath. Large utility room/entry with plenty of storage. Attached covered carport, ample parking, and detached garage/shop perfect for any hobbyist. This is an ideal vacation home or year round residence, with the perfect setup for entertaining or quiet walks on the beach, soaking in sightings of whales, sea lions, seals & eagles. Close to Bellingham for shopping and amenities.
nearby_schools: Lummi Elementary School, Lummi High School, Ferndale School District

text: Investor Alert in Downtown Bellingham. Discover the potential of this condo located in the heart of downtown Bellingham. Perfectly positioned within walking distance to all amenities, this property presents a prime opportunity for renovation and investment. Ideal downtown location, steps away from shops, dining, and entertainment. This space is ready for a full renovation, that offers solid bones and a canvas for customization. Condo is an Estate sale, being sold As Is.

Beautiful Birch Bay Village quality full custom lakefront home. 130ft of waterfront, on quiet & very friendly Cul de Sac. Great room design w/BIG kitchen & lots of storage. Granite surfaces, solid Oak custom cabinetry throughout, Oversized garage, new roof, siding, floors, paint, appliances, furnace, AC, H/W tank, gas firepit, garage heat, lighting, tilework & more in Dec 2016. Bromic outdoor overhead heaters under spacious covered lakefront patio = year-round comfort. Fenced yard, Golf cart garage entry. Jacuzzi tub in master suite. Village has a (brand new) marina, golf course & 24/7 gated, manned security, clubhouse, Pickleball & Tennis Courts, heated pool. The list goes on! Come Home to a Vacation, Come Home to Birch Bay Village .

Discover this stunning custom-built home within walking distance of Lake Padden and near Galbraith Mountain! Featuring 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, it boasts an open kitchen, dog wash station, and a spacious covered deck with a hot tub. The downstairs area, with tall ceilings, is perfect for a media room. Enjoy ample RV and boat parking, plus a back roll-up garage door leading to a patio for seamless indoor-outdoor living. With solar panels, a sprinkler system for the flowers, and views of the bay and Chuckanut Mountain, this home offers no shortage of outdoor hangout spaces. The fully fenced yard adorned with fruit trees makes this home an absolute must-see!

Delightful home in this sought after 55+ community park. Perfectly located within walking distance to Fairhaven's shops and amenities, interurban trail and an abundancy of city parks. This lovely home is at the end of a dead-end street, providing privacy and seclusion. The primary bedroom has a huge en-suite bathroom with double vanity, corner tub and large walk-in shower cubicle. Good size 2nd bedroom and full 2nd bathroom. Kitchen has new quartz countertops and new tiled back-splash, with dining area or recreational area adjacent. Spacious living room and good size office or could be a separate dining room. Recently painted throughout making this home bright and fresh. The rear yard has a lovely decked area to relax. A gem!

This beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom rambler is nestled on just over an acre at the end of a quite road. With a spacious layout and a host of desirable features, this property is perfect for those seeking comfort, convenience, and a touch of country charm. Bright and airy living spaces with plenty of natural light. Enjoy central a/c in the warm summer months and a brand new furnace! Large detached shop offering endless possibilities for hobbies and additional storage. Dedicated covered space for RVs, boats, or additional vehicles. Enjoy outdoor living featuring a large deck over looking a private acre of manicured lawn, flower beds, and surrounded by trees for ultimate privacy.

Charming Southside of Bellingham top floor end unit in the sought after Cypress Condo Complex. Enjoy the abundant light, spacious kitchen, and ample full bathroom with in unit stackable washer and dryer. Step out onto the patio and enjoy the evening breeze as you take in the South Hills and Chuckanut Mountain. Additional storage unit just a few steps from the door. Additional amenities include secure building, elevator, gated entry, fitness center and outdoor covered bike storage. Easy walk or bike ride to Joe's Garden, REI, groceries, shopping, dining, and local trails.

Clean and affordable home on fully fenced lot! Where to start on this exceptional property. First, you get a spacious 924 square feet 2 bedroom home, with fresh interior paint, newer flooring, remodeled bathroom, new hot water heater, all new plumbing and a free standing woodstove for a great second heat source. Second, we head outside and find a fully fenced 6 foot chain link fence with separate garden area and separate dog area! Plant a beautiful garden and don't worry about critters getting in there and eating all your hard work! Huge covered deck brings you outdoors in any kind of weather. Wait, we haven't talked about the wood shed and 2 other large sheds with enough storage for anyone! All this is for $199, 000?! Yep! Ready, set, go!

Welcome to Whispering Meadows. Immaculate new construction home in one of the newest developments in Nooksack. This 4 bed 2.25 bath has it all. Open living with lots of natural light & a cozy fireplace creates a warm & inviting atmosphere. Kitchen features quartz counters, brushed nickel hardware, & SS appliances which offers a modern & stylish space. The main floor master bedroom features vaulted ceilings, huge walk-in closet, & a double vanity in the ensuite bath. Remaining 3 bedrooms upstairs & one of them could be easily used as a bonus room. Ductless mini splits to keep you cool in the summer & warm in the winter. Lets not forget about the deck & private backyard, perfect for enjoying outdoor activities. House is not in the flood zone!

Fabulous single level home is ready to debut its' glow up! Experience all the shiny new features youve been looking for, all on a huge, fully fenced corner lot! Recent updates include new lighting, fresh interior paint, new windows & slider, modern interior doors/hardware & updated plumbing throughout for extra peace of mind. Your refurbished kitchen is ready for action with all new floors and counters + a newer double oven! Complete w/sparkling new bath flooring & plush carpet in the additional BRs, this home has been thoughtfully renovated from top to bottom. In addition to your sauna, your yard is the star of the show with garden space, fruit trees & XL shed (that doubles as a shop)! Dont miss your chance to own this fabulous property!

Enjoy stunning bay, island, mountain, and city views from this 2-bedroom, 1.75-bath, 1, 432 sq ft condo. Located in a secure, 55+ community with 15 units, it features an elevator from covered parking to your front door. The kitchen has updated appliances, interior paint, new carpet, and the dining area offers expansive views. The covered deck is perfect for relaxing and entertaining while enjoying spectacular sunsets. The spacious living room includes a gas fireplace, and the primary bedroom has an ensuite bath. Additional features include a stackable washer/dryer, ample storage, and a large shared workshop. Close to WWU, Sehome Arboretum, and Downtown Bellingham.

Indulge in contemporary elegance at 943 Verde Loop, a meticulously crafted residence in Bellingham. With 3 beds and 2.25 baths, this home seamlessly blends modern design with PNW charm. This spacious home features an open-concept layout, ideal for both entertaining and everyday living. Upgraded fixtures, hardwood floors, and a gourmet kitchen create a culinary haven. The primary bedroom offers luxury and scenic views. Enjoy outdoor living in the fenced backyard, perfect for gatherings. Stunning mountain and golf course vistas capture the essence of West Coast living. Conveniently located near parks, schools, and shopping, seize this opportunity to embrace quintessential Bellingham.

Roosevelt neighborhood charmer, walking distance to Trader Joes & Barkley Village, shops, restaurants & parks. Plentiful windows create bright living spaces, several doors lead to fully fenced private back yard with hot tub & garden shed. Entertain + relax in your lush garden with fruit trees & flowering plants. Primary Bedroom on main level, abundant built-in storage, kitchen pantry, mini-split with A/C. Laundry/mud room, spacious 1-car garage + 2 car driveway + plentiful parking on quiet street. New water heater 1-2024, new sewer line 12-2022. Walk score: 71; bike score: 76, near Railroad Trail. Potential ADU opportunity - verify with City. Could also be a great rental property. Buyer to confirm schools.

Geneva Rambler situated on a 12, 000+ SF lot on a serene & luxurious cul-de-sac. This 3BD/2BA home offers many desirable features like finished-in-place oak floors through much of the main living area. The living room is flooded in natural light while enjoying partial lake views & access to a large, sunrise-facing deck. Entertain in the dining room or appoint it as a den, & relish the flexibility of the dine-in kitchen. Spacious Primary Suite w/full bath & walk-in closet. Wide-open 3-car garage offers over 800 SF for all the vehicles & toys, a shop, or the ultimate home gym. Minutes to multiple parks, beaches, Stimpson Nature Reserve, Whole Foods & I-5. Make some minor updates to enhance your lifestyle & build equity at 4725 Austin Ct.
Latitude 49, lot 49

Welcome to 455 3rd St, Sumas, WA 98295! Nestled in the heart of Sumas, this charming single-family home boasts 2 spacious bedrooms and 1.0 bathroom across 1172 square feet. Enjoy the convenience of being close to the Canadian border, offering endless opportunities for exploration and adventure. With its cozy ambiance and desirable location, this property is an ideal choice for those seeking comfort and accessibility. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make this house your home

$5, 000 Seller Credit for new Kitchen Counters. Elegant & inviting, updated single-level home nestled in the beautiful Orchard Crest community of Ferndale. This meticulously maintained residence situated on a huge lot offers an inviting open floor plan with tall vaulted ceilings and skylights for lots of natural light. Step onto Brazilian cherry hardwood floors and enjoy marble and travertine tile throughout. A/C, a new roof with a 50-year warranty, ensuring comfort and peace of mind. Solid wood doors, granite vanities, and custom touches add to the home's distinctive appeal. Fully fenced backyard features a large 2-level deck, recently stained, perfect for gatherings and relaxation. Appliances are included, making this home move-in ready.

Welcome to 6120 Aquarius Ave, a charming and well maintained 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom home in Ferndale. With 968 square feet of comfortable living space, this property offers an inviting open layout on the main floor, seamlessly connecting the kitchen and living room. Upstairs, you'll find all three bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a conveniently located laundry area, providing ease of living. Step outside through the sliding door to a spacious backyard with a gravel patio area, perfect for relaxation and entertaining. The property also features a 1-car garage, RV parking, and a new water heater. Just minutes from Skyline Elementary School. Don't miss out on one of the most affordable single family homes in the county!

Situated in the vibrant core of Bellingham is a recently constructed modern duplex, completed in 2022. Within each meticulously crafted unit, discover 2 bedrooms and 1 bath featuring a double vanity. Enjoy personalized comfort with a mini split offering both heating and cooling options. Parking is hassle-free with one covered spot and an additional uncovered space for each unit, complemented by a convenient outside storage unit for your outdoor essentials. The kitchen is a chef's dream, stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and cabinets that close with a gentle touch. Enhancing the overall allure, this chic duplex showcases Provenza vinyl floors. Welcome to contemporary living in the heart of Bellingham!

2.82 pastoral and view acreage on Lummi Island with panoramic southwest views of other San Juan Islands and Rosario Strait from every inch of this fantastic property: big sky vistas, captivating southwest light, and beautiful grassy plains. There are very few of these buildable acreages left in this area. Excellent center island location, which allows you to walk to farm stands, post office, beaches, library, restaurant, and school! The property has corners marked, a driveway easement is in place from the private road for development, a shared well is available, and a septic drain field is in place.
nearby_schools: Lummi Elementary School, Lummi High School, Ferndale School District

text: This beautiful home is nestled in serene surroundings, this property is perfect for outdoor enthusiasts. Imagine immersing yourself in nature's wonderland, steps from your front door. You are only a few minutes from Galbraith Mountain Trails, Lake Padden, and Lake Samish. Within 10 minutes, enjoy Fairhaven, and Downtown Bellingham's vibrant communities with their shops, dining, entertainment. Convivence is the key, with easy access to I-5 for a smooth commute. This thoroughly designed home has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and sits on .84-acre lot. Recent upgrades include a new heat pump, Generac generator, exterior and interior paint, added pantry, and extra parking. Don't miss this incredible property combining tranquility and convivence.

Step into this inviting 2-bedroom condo nestled in The Cypress Place Condominiums. Welcomed by a courtyard view, this home boasts a bright and efficient layout designed to enhance everyday living. A well-appointed kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances and granite counters, a cozy living room with an electric fireplace, and access to a patio perfect for relaxation or entertaining guests. Additional highlights include in-unit laundry, ss well as two designated parking spaces and a storage closet. Enjoy the amenities of Cypress Condominiums including secure entry, elevators, an exercise room, and bike storage - all in a great location close to WWU, trails, shopping, and restaurants.

Large double lot located in the lakeside and golf course community of Sudden Valley. Wonderful south facing property with large evergreens in the neighborhood. The property is a gentle down-sloping lot, making it conducive for a home plan with main level living and a daylight basement below. Plenty of room for a 3-car garage in your house plan as well! Loads of elbow room here! There is potential access below the property coming up from Honeycomb Lane for utilities or a lower driveway to a garage area. Buyer to verify.

NEW CONSTRUCTION! Live the PNW lakeside dream from home. The property offers quality design and an open concept floorplan with 4 livable bedrooms, or a 2 bed w/ 2+ office/rec rooms, and 2.5 baths. Premium finishes include LVP flooring, AC, tiled shower, hardiplank siding etc. Enjoy entertaining in your spacious living room w cozy gas fireplace or host outdoors on your covered patio. Situated on a private lot and backing up to nearby trails, this is what outdoor enthusiast dreams are made of. With access to all of Glenhavens amenities including its own club house, parks, pool, and trails to Reed and Cain Lake, this home is one you dont want to miss out on. Up to $5, 000 Buyer Credit with The Pysden Team at CrossCoutry Mortgage available.

Welcome to the architecturally award winning 10th & Taylor Condominiums with Westerly bay views! Experience the ultimate lifestyle with an easy stroll to historic Fairhaven Village, just steps away from Bellingham's iconic waterfront boardwalk and across from the Chrysalis Inn & Spa, featuring one of Bellingham's finest restaurants. The owner, who purchased this condo at the foundation stage of construction, completely redesigned the interior with custom high end cabinetry, appliances, flooring, doors, AC and in floor radiant heat and much more. Enjoy a rare level entry from private alley parking to your front door, and a gated garage for your two cars and storage accessed by an elevator. This is an opportunity to own one of the best!

This home feels better than new! A charming one-level 3 bed, 2 bath corner lot with fresh landscaping and new outdoor living area. This home features stunning hardwood floors and fresh paint throughout interior and exterior. The spacious living room boasts vaulted ceilings and a cozy fireplace, perfect for relaxing. The modern kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances. The primary suite offers a walk-in closet and an attached bathroom. Located just a short walk from Lynden Middle School and nearby parks, this home is ideal for anyone. Come schedule a private tour today!

Beautifully well maintained 2, 800 sqft custom home in a cul-de-sac with peaceful views! Main floor living with a vaulted great room and an open kitchen with quality hardwoods throughout. A massive deck wraps the back of the house, so private with views of a pristine untouched greenspace. Off the great room rests a large primary suite, 2nd bedroom/office plus full bath. The lower level consists of a second primary with ensuite bath, family room, additional bedroom & workshop with a pre-built workbench & tons of room for storage. Plus, a spacious waterproof covered patio off the lower level with a fenced backyard, storage shed & garden space. This home offers comfort & easy living, nestled in a serene setting... a private oasis in town!

Wonderful 3+ bdrm, 3.5 bath, 3052 sq ft Lyndal Cedar home in rural setting, immaculate condition.Easy access to I-5 & Canadian Border. Outdoor living area overlooking 6 manicured acres w/ pond perfect for those private parties and afternoon BBQs. Living room with vaulted ceilings, lots of windows, wood fireplace. Kitchen has granite counters, custom cabinets, skylights, Brazilian hardwood floors. Main bedroom has cozy fireplace, french doors opening to the private hot tub and view of your very own park like setting. Main bath has soaker tub, tiled shower and walk-in closet. 2 other large bedrooms, office, flex room could be separate living quarters. Oversized 2 car garage, 30x36 shop, 300 Ft asphalt drive with covered parking for RV'S

Nestled in a serene, private location with stunning views of Mt. Baker, this charming 2-bedroom, 1.5-bath manufactured home offers comfortable living in a 55+ park, in a central location. Recently upgraded with new sheeting and a composition roof, this cozy 1296 sqft home is move-in ready, awaiting your personal touch to truly make it feel like home. While move-in ready, this property presents an exciting opportunity for personalization, allowing you to infuse your personality and style effortlessly. With its attractive price point and desirable location, this gem is a perfect fit for savvy buyers seeking affordability.

Nature Lovers Paradise! Welcome to this beautiful 3, 100 sqft home in the middle of an outdoor sanctuary with various types of trees, fruit and wildlife. Enter through a tree-lined private drive which opens up to a 15 acre oasis that extends into Lake Fazon. Vaulted ceiling with extensive windows will delight you with the beauty that surrounds w mountain and lake views. This 4 bdrm, 4 barm home has large Douglas Fir posts and beams throughout, a big kitchen w granite countertops w island that opens up to the dining and living rm. The downstairs family rm has a kitchen for a potential mother-in-law suite. Grab your waders and go duck hunt or fish in your back yard! Only 15 minutes to Bellingham, this is a very special one-of-a-kind property.

Situated in the heart of Edgemoor, this 1988 quality built custom home offers tranquil living in one of the most sought after neighborhoods in Bellingham. Meticulously maintained in its original state, this residence radiates a classic charm that never goes out of style. Built on a spacious lot amidst a picturesque backdrop of mature trees and easy-care landscaping. Step through the dining room french doors to a sunny deck overlooking the scenic landscape and fully fenced yard, ideal for outdoor living and entertaining. The main-level primary suite and two upper-level bedrooms, each offer full-size bathrooms and walk-in closets to ensure luxurious comfort. 2 car garage. New roof and furnace. Only two owners since the house was built.

Modern living wrapped in rustic charm! Situated on 4.47 acres of fully fenced rolling pasture land, this lovingly restored 1910 farmhouse is that hard to find mini-farm you've been searching for. Recent updates include metal roofing on all structures, fencing, all new SS appliances, new high efficiency furnace and air-conditioning, new enclosed back porch and steps and an exceptionally well crafted cedar post and beam deck enclosure with French doors leading from the spacious living room. Well manicured orchard with 9 fruit trees and lush landscaping together with a barn with stables and huge loft area plus 3 attached garages, a carport and shop space. Truly one of the most charming properties on the market today and an exceptional value.

Rare find, end unit! Tucked in a serene neighborhood off Alabama in the highly desirable Sand Dollar Village Condos! This beautifully cared for one-level home has 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths and an open-concept floor plan! Stylishly updated kitchen with oodles of choice Hickory cabinets, pantry and large eat-in counter. Hickory cabinets in bathrooms as well. Great for entertaining; a vaulted ceiling and gas fireplace adds that homey feel. Retreat to a cozy, covered back patio, enough room to BBQ & host a few guests! Large closets in each bedroom & in the hallway keep you organized. You'll benefit from included yard care; put your feet up! Just minutes to nearby Whatcom Falls Park, downtown Bellingham shops, galleries, WWU & nearby hospital.
